---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="contrato-social"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-social-contract"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-container--wide wheat-grid wheat-grid--cols-2 wheat-items-center wheat-gap-12">
        <div class="wheat-space-y-6 wheat-space-y-8@md">
            <span class="trigo-chapter wheat-contract-chapter wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase">
                El Contrato Social
            </span>
            <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-4xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-contract-title">Leyes de Grano</h2>
            <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-contract-desc">
                Cuando tienes un granero, necesitas protegerlo. Cuando tienes vecinos con hambre,
                necesitas leyes.
            </p>
            <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-contract-desc">
                El Código de Hammurabi, una de las primeras leyes escritas, no habla de libertad.
                Habla de deudas, de robos de grano, de canales de riego. <ShareableQuote
                    quote="La justicia nació para administrar la cosecha."
                />
            </p>
            <div class="wheat-contract-quote-box wheat-p-6">
                <p class="wheat-italic wheat-contract-quote-text">
                    "Si un hombre tiene una deuda de grano y no tiene dinero para pagarla, entregará
                    a su hijo o hija como esclavo."
                </p>
                <p class="wheat-text-xs wheat-contract-quote-author wheat-mt-2 wheat-uppercase wheat-tracking-widest">
                    - Código de Hammurabi, 1750 a.C.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="wheat-relative wheat-contract-visual-container wheat-p-8 wheat-flex wheat-flex-col wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-rounded wheat-border">
            <div class="wheat-contract-tablet wheat-rounded wheat-flex wheat-flex-col wheat-gap-1 wheat-p-4 wheat-overflow-hidden wheat-relative">
                <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-contract-tablet-overlay"></div>

                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--full"></div>
                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--2-3"></div>
                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--full wheat-mt-2"></div>
                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--3-4"></div>
                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--full wheat-mt-2"></div>
                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--1-2"></div>
                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--full wheat-mt-2"></div>
                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--full"></div>
                <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-line wheat-contract-tablet-line--4-5 wheat-mt-2"></div>

                <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-contract-tablet-seal wheat-rounded-full wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center">
                    <div class="wheat-contract-tablet-seal-inner wheat-rounded-full"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="wheat-mt-6 wheat-text-xs wheat-contract-tablet-caption wheat-font-mono wheat-text-center">
                TABLILLA ADMINISTRATIVA<br />Uruk, 3100 a.C.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-social-contract {
        color: #e7e5e4;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(120, 53, 4, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-contract-chapter {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-contract-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-contract-desc {
        color: #d6d3d1;
    }
    .wheat-contract-quote-box {
        background-color: #0c0a09;
        border-left: 2px solid #b45309;
    }
    .wheat-contract-quote-text {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-contract-quote-author {
        color: #d97706;
    }
    .wheat-contract-visual-container {
        height: 24rem;
        background-color: #292524;
        border-color: #292524;
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    }
    .wheat-contract-tablet {
        width: 12rem;
        height: 16rem;
        background-color: #44403c;
        box-shadow: inset 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-overlay {
        opacity: 0.5;
        mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-line {
        height: 4px;
        background-color: rgba(87, 83, 78, 0.5);
        border-radius: 0.25rem;
    }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-line--full { width: 100%; }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-line--2-3 { width: 66.666667%; }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-line--3-4 { width: 75%; }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-line--1-2 { width: 50%; }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-line--4-5 { width: 80%; }
    
    .wheat-contract-tablet-seal {
        bottom: 1rem;
        right: 1rem;
        width: 2rem;
        height: 2rem;
        border: 2px solid rgba(120, 53, 4, 0.3);
    }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-seal-inner {
        width: 1rem;
        height: 1rem;
        background-color: rgba(120, 53, 4, 0.5);
    }
    .wheat-contract-tablet-caption {
        color: #78716c;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-space-y-8\@md > * + * {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
